name: Company-custom_important
options:
You have to ‘clear’ the Standard Tax Invoice (B2B) from ZATCA in real-time and then share it with the buyers as a legally valid e-invoice.
You are required to report simplified invoices (B2C) to ZATCA within 24 hours from the time of generation.
Non Reported invoices will be automatically reported to Zatca at midnight or every hour!
